      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions replicated in simulation within stated measurement uncertainty; fluid properties matched to blood analog used in bench tests.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles approximated by fully-developed assumption rather than measured profiles; blood analog viscosity matched but non-Newtonian shear-thinning behaviour not incorporated. Achieved level 2."
    },
